summary: This new code file, contact.html, contributes a contact page to the system. It includes a header titled "Contact" and provides email addresses for contacting the team. Additionally, it contains a menu option for navigating to the contact page, allowing users to easily access the contact information. The file also includes a home button for quick navigation back to the home page. Overall, this file enhances the user experience by providing easy access to contact information within the system.
